
# 🧪 Random Forest Validation

> A concise, reproducible walkthrough to validate a Random Forest classifier with proper splits, cross-validation, and metrics.

---

## 📌 Objective
Validate a **Random Forest** model on a tabular dataset with a clean, reproducible pipeline:

- Data preparation & label encoding  
- Stratified train/test split  
- Cross-validation  
- Hyperparameter tuning  
- Model evaluation (accuracy, precision, recall, F1, confusion matrix)

